<H2>What Can LSI Do For Me Today? </H2>
       <LI><FONT size=5>Relevance Feedback.</FONT></LI>
       <BR><BR>
       <LI><FONT size=5>Textual Coherence.</FONT></LI>
 	  <UL>
		<LI><FONT size=4>LSI can look at the semantic relationships within a text to 
		calculate the degree of topical coherence between its constituent parts</FONT></LI>
	  </UL>
       <BR><BR>
       <LI><FONT size=5>Automated Writing Assessment.</FONT></LI>
 	  <UL>
		<LI><FONT size=4>can be used as a kind of automated grading system</FONT></LI>
	  </UL>
       <BR><BR>
       <LI><FONT size=5>Information Filtering.</FONT></LI>
 	  <UL>
		<LI><FONT size=4>LSI is potentially a powerful customizable technology for filtering spam</FONT></LI>
